<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00371/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>数组硅胶制冰模具，任何由其制造成的方冰在融化过程都会不间断发出近似人类孩童的尖叫声。液面或冰面上端会以水为原料形成一只高举着的微型手臂，直至冰块彻底融化。冰块消融成的水将在约莫十五分钟后转化为人类血液。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>2020/8/20<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>广东省深圳市一间塑胶模具制造工厂<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>存放于Area-CN-07标准物品收容保险柜中<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>自回收到的第二十三副异常模具夹格中回收到一张便条，疑似指明这批异常产品的实际制造者。——研究员汪唐宋</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Cheers！致每一位为我们献上美酒的Mr.Ice。你肯定要为此下地狱了！</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00371" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00371" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00371-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rye-travis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3290685); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3290685&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610249713" alt="Rye Travis" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3290685)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rye-travis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3290685); return false;">Rye Travis</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1597930110 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">20 Aug 2020 13:28</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00365/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一个由水泥浇筑成的斜坡，坡度约45度。任何物体自其底部沿坡面上升至顶部后将会获得约████倍的原速度。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>巴音郭楞蒙古自治州附近<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>被整体移动至Site-CN-██异常物理学研究部门<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>是哪个白痴把全速的摩托车开上去的？要是让我找到你，实验翼区的全部重建费用必从你工资里扣。</em>——Dr.Kleiner</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00365" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00365" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00365-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kayo-kesr-aquas" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5232386); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5232386&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610249713" alt="Kayo_Kesr_Aquas" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5232386)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kayo-kesr-aquas" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5232386); return false;">Kayo_Kesr_Aquas</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1597821914 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">19 Aug 2020 07:25</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00124/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一把经过异常改造的███牌AK-47水弹枪，当使用项目射出水弹时，水弹会转变为7.62mm步枪弹。值得注意的是子弹在打出后是未击发的状态。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong> ███市一市民家中<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>放置于Site-██异常武器收容室中<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>无限子弹补给？</em>——Dr.pigeon</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00124" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00124" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00124-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpionidaslaughter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6306406); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6306406&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610249713" alt="ScorpionidaSlaughter" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6306406)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpionidaslaughter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6306406); return false;">ScorpionidaSlaughter</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1588036841 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">28 Apr 2020 01:20</span></p>
